<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.2">
<l>nāraṇaṉ muḻuvē ḻulakukku nātaṉ vētamayaṉ</l>
<l>kāraṇaṅ kiricai karuma mivaimutalva ṉentai</l>
<l>cīraṇaṅ kamarar piṟarpala runtoḻu tēttaniṉṟu</l>
<l>vāraṇat taimarup pocitta pirāṉeṉ mātavaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Nārāyaṇa, the leader of the whole seven worlds, the one who consists of Vedas,</l>
<l>the one who is the first of causes, actions [and] karmas(?), our father,</l>
<l>the lord who broke the elephant’s tusk, standing while the excellent awesome immortals</l>
<l>and many others worship [and] praise [him], is my Mādava.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
